The '''bob-tailed weaver''' ('''''Brachycope anomala''''') is a species of [[bird]] in the family [[Ploceidae]]. It is [[monotypic]] within the genus '''''Brachycope'''''.<ref name = "ITIS"/>
It is native to the [[Congo Basin]].<ref name="iucn status 11 November 2021" />

